	<div id="post-52849" class="post standard site-container marg-b-50 post-52849 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-culture category-gamelife tag-people tag-retrogames tag-special-feature" data-js='article' itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article" data-id="52849">

